    "e7e0dfba-bcb1-4462-9dbd-7c457052869a": {
      "type": "custom-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "52414ad7-f160-41dd-83f9-9279ecbd005f": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em><strong>Q: Paez is known for its casual and versatile shoes that are perfect for the beach. Can you describe your go-to outfit for a day of surfing and working?</strong></em></p><p><br/><strong>A: </strong>I love the slip-on style of Paez shoes, the Mocs which makes them perfect for a day of surfing and working. On a typical day, I'll pair my Paez shoes with board shorts and a t-shirt for surfing, and then swap the board shorts for jeans or shorts for work. I like to keep it simple and practical, so I can focus on the task at hand.</p><p><em><strong><br/>Q: What do you think distinguishes your surfboards from others on the market, and how do you approach design?</strong></em></p><p><br/><strong>A:</strong> When it comes to my surfboards, I'm all about the perfect blend of performance and aesthetics. I meticulously consider the needs of the surfer and the surf conditions, and I take great pride in every step of the construction process to deliver a top-notch product that stands out from the rest of the market.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
