    "4a0bdaf6-e6df-41f1-ad2f-f4d9177cd7d0": {
      "type": "custom-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "40444b61-ed84-461f-8ffb-eb12a064b562": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em><strong>Q: Describe a day's work for us. What is the most fun?</strong></em></p><p><br/><strong>A: </strong>Every day is a new adventure for me. Some days I'm out delivering boards, while others I'm hanging out with friends at the factory. But the most fun is when I can start my day off surfing with my colleagues and then head to the factory to continue shaping boards. I absolutely love what I do, so it doesn't feel like work at all.</p><p><em><strong><br/>Q: What's the cutest project you've ever been involved in?</strong></em></p><p><br/><strong>A:</strong> I recently had the pleasure of opening a new factory with two of my friends, where we produce not only our own brands but also other brands from around the world. It's been an incredibly cute project, and we're having a blast working together.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
