      "blocks": {
        "ccab4737-cc1d-495f-b5e8-1edd116ac654": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em><strong>Q: How do you manage to integrate creativity into your daily life?</strong></em></p><p><br/><strong>A:</strong> Creativity is always at the forefront of my mind. Each board is unique and requires individual thought and consideration. From the colors and patterns to the materials and construction, I love imagining a product and then seeing it come to life.</p><p><em><strong><br/>Q: How do you maintain a balance between professional and personal life while following a clear passion for surfing and surfboard shaping, and what advice would you give to others looking to do the same?</strong></em></p><p><br/><strong>A:</strong> Balancing my personal life with my passion for surfing and shaping can be challenging, but luckily my flexible schedule allows me to make it work. My advice for others is to seek out a community of like-minded individuals who can share knowledge and help you improve. I've learned so much from others and it</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
